Hey, Qian.

56
00:03:10,560 --> 00:03:11,400
Sang Yan!

57
00:03:11,710 --> 00:03:13,280
Wish you a happy wedding.

58
00:03:14,120 --> 00:03:15,240
Thanks.

59
00:03:15,520 --> 00:03:16,590
Come on. Take your seats.

60
00:03:18,000 --> 00:03:20,560
Duan Jiaxu, you quite enjoyed yourself.

61
00:03:20,870 --> 00:03:22,400
You didn't even tell me you were here.

62
00:03:22,710 --> 00:03:23,960
Call me big brother

63
