64
00:03:27,710 --> 00:03:29,030
Uncle gave that to me.

65
00:03:29,840 --> 00:03:31,310
Give it back.

66
00:03:31,560 --> 00:03:33,590
Thank you, big brother.

67
00:03:33,590 --> 00:03:34,590
You're welcome.

68
00:03:35,470 --> 00:03:36,080
Give it back.

69
00:03:36,080 --> 00:03:36,800
Oh, brother.

70
00:03:36,800 --> 00:03:37,630
Give it back.

71
00:03:38,080 --> 00:03:40,120
From now on, you'll be my big brother.

72
00:03:40,590 --> 00:03:43,150
Hey, are you insane?

73
00:03:43,190 --> 00:03:44,560
I'm not.

74
00:03:44,680 --> 00:03:46,120
Thank you for your concern.

75
00:03:46,360 --> 00:03:47,590
You guys, that's enough.

76
00:03:48,430 --> 00:03:49,190
Brother.

77
00:03:49,190 --> 00:03:49,870
Kid,

78
00:03:49,870 --> 00:03:51,430
don't call me brother now.

79
00:03:51,470 --> 00:03:52,590
This word

80
00:03:52,590 --> 00:03:53,520
makes me sick.

81
00:03:53,590 --> 00:03:54,560
- Qian Fei.
- Yep.

82
00:03:54,560 --> 00:03:55,710
I'm going to the bathroom.

83
00:03:55,870 --> 00:03:56,520
Go ahead.

84
00:04:08,310 --> 00:04:10,560
Zhizhi, Dad bought you chocolate cake.

85
00:04:10,560 --> 00:04:11,750
It's in the fridge.

86
00:04:11,750 --> 00:04:13,080
Eat it when you're back tonight.

87
00:04:13,190 --> 00:04:14,560
Mm, okay.

88
00:04:16,720 --> 00:04:17,630
Who is Zhizhi?

89
00:04:18,830 --> 00:04:19,630
Why do you ask?

90
00:04:20,190 --> 00:04:21,120
Is that your brother?

91
00:04:21,510 --> 00:04:22,750
Nonsense.

92
00:04:23,190 --> 00:04:23,950
It's me.

93
00:04:24,750 --> 00:04:25,950
It's my nickname.

94
00:04:26,870 --> 00:04:28,120
Who usually calls you that?

95
00:04:29,310 --> 00:04:31,430
People close to me.

96
00:04:34,000 --> 00:04:35,920
Then, who is "Brother No.2"?

97
00:04:37,160 --> 00:04:39,000
He's No.1. You're No.2.

98
00:04:39,000 --> 00:04:41,000
Why am I No.2?

99
00:04:41,720 --> 00:04:43,240
Because you're older than him.

100
00:04:43,560 --> 00:04:44,920
So, you're No.2.

101
00:04:44,950 --> 00:04:46,190
Any problem?

102
00:04:46,270 --> 00:04:47,560
But I look younger.

103
00:04:48,680 --> 00:04:49,600
Jiaxu,

104
00:04:50,510 --> 00:04:53,360
