105
00:04:53,950 --> 00:04:55,720
Did girls complain about your age

106
00:04:55,720 --> 00:04:57,600
when you had blind dates?

107
00:04:58,190 --> 00:04:58,950
Blind dates?

108
00:04:59,270 --> 00:04:59,720
Mm.

109
00:05:00,070 --> 00:05:01,390
Oh, right.

110
00:05:02,000 --> 00:05:04,750
You asked your brother and me
to have blind dates.

111
00:05:06,390 --> 00:05:08,120
I just want you

112
00:05:08,120 --> 00:05:09,950
