113
00:05:10,120 --> 00:05:11,800
Then, you'll be confident.

114
00:05:11,800 --> 00:05:13,390
But your brother doesn't want that.

115
00:05:13,800 --> 00:05:14,600
How about this?

116
00:05:15,070 --> 00:05:17,160
You and I will go together.

117
00:05:21,560 --> 00:05:22,360
What's wrong?

118
00:05:22,390 --> 00:05:23,950
You don't want to go?

119
00:05:24,800 --> 00:05:26,360
How can I go with you?

120
00:05:27,160 --> 00:05:28,310
Anyway,

121
00:05:28,560 --> 00:05:30,750
people will complain if you take me.

122
00:05:30,830 --> 00:05:31,630
About what?

123
00:05:32,000 --> 00:05:33,720
About taking a daughter for blind dates.

124
00:05:35,390 --> 00:05:36,800
Ask him to shut up.

125
00:05:37,000 --> 00:05:38,870
You haven't enjoyed yourself.

126
00:05:38,870 --> 00:05:39,480
Come on.

127
00:05:39,480 --> 00:05:40,510
I won't drink anymore.

128
00:05:40,510 --> 00:05:41,750
Let's keep drinking. Come on.

129
00:05:41,750 --> 00:05:42,360
Brother.

130
00:05:42,360 --> 00:05:42,630
Huh?

131
00:05:43,190 --> 00:05:44,000
Kid,

132
00:05:44,190 --> 00:05:45,040
you go home.

133
00:05:45,160 --> 00:05:45,950
Go home without me.

134
00:05:46,000 --> 00:05:47,430
Just go. Don't worry.

135
00:05:47,430 --> 00:05:48,070
Okay.

136
00:05:48,120 --> 00:05:49,560
- Come on.
- Be careful.

137
00:05:49,560 --> 00:05:50,270
Let's go.

138
00:05:50,310 --> 00:05:51,120
Come on.

139
00:05:52,920 --> 00:05:53,390
Let's go.

140
00:05:53,920 --> 00:05:54,800
I'll get you home.

141
00:05:55,800 --> 00:05:57,950
Jiaxu, don't bother.

142
00:05:57,950 --> 00:05:59,630
You should go with them.

143
00:06:00,920 --> 00:06:02,950
Helping someone else may bother me.

144
00:06:03,070 --> 00:06:04,190
But getting you home

145
00:06:04,390 --> 00:06:05,190
