195
00:08:58,030 --> 00:09:01,700
♪The moon glows
and I think you'll get it♪

196
00:09:02,780 --> 00:09:06,650
♪I can't tell how warm it is♪

197
00:09:07,130 --> 00:09:11,330
♪No one but you can feel this moment♪

198
00:09:12,140 --> 00:09:16,370
♪I think feelings are indescribable♪

