Hey, Duan Jiaxu.

207
00:09:53,360 --> 00:09:54,640
Don't keep me guessing, okay?

208
00:09:54,640 --> 00:09:55,520
Just tell me.

209
00:09:55,520 --> 00:09:57,160
What kind of guy?

210
00:09:57,670 --> 00:09:58,950
A Mr. Charming.

211
00:10:01,310 --> 00:10:02,670
As far as I see,

212
00:10:03,030 --> 00:10:04,190
he must be

213
