216
00:10:10,550 --> 00:10:11,790
Come on, bro.

217
00:10:12,070 --> 00:10:13,120
She...

218
00:10:13,240 --> 00:10:15,120
Was she just talking about you?

219
00:10:15,120 --> 00:10:16,950
Don't be ridiculous.

220
00:10:17,310 --> 00:10:19,160
Hey, think about it.

221
00:10:19,280 --> 00:10:21,000
I've never seen this girl.

222
00:10:21,160 --> 00:10:22,280
But you think carefully.

223
00:10:22,280 --> 00:10:23,950
Maybe she was just talking about you.

224
00:10:23,950 --> 00:10:25,950
I don't think so.

225
00:10:26,550 --> 00:10:27,360
But...

226
00:10:29,640 --> 00:10:31,000
