230
00:10:34,710 --> 00:10:36,600
Have a good trip tomorrow.

231
00:10:37,070 --> 00:10:38,000
I'll see you around.

232
00:10:38,000 --> 00:10:38,760
Wait.

233
00:10:39,480 --> 00:10:40,760
I'll ask you one more time.

234
00:10:41,160 --> 00:10:42,310
Do you really think

235
00:10:42,310 --> 00:10:43,670
I'm like Mr. Charming?

236
00:10:43,670 --> 00:10:44,310
Yes.

237
00:10:44,310 --> 00:10:45,030
You're just like him.

238
00:10:45,030 --> 00:10:47,120
100 percent, sweetheart.

239
00:11:04,160 --> 00:11:08,670
♪If we meet again, don't hug me♪

240
00:11:08,730 --> 00:11:11,770
♪I don't want it this way♪

241
00:11:11,770 --> 00:11:15,390
♪I can't see or force a smile♪

242
00:11:15,390 --> 00:11:18,870
♪I'll just forget it♪

243
00:11:19,130 --> 00:11:23,070
♪If I can't cover
the corners of my eyes♪

244
00:11:23,540 --> 00:11:26,660
♪How will my tears roll down?♪

245
